          Ingredients

          
            
              frac14


              pound slab or thickcut bacon diced
            
            
              1


              medium yellow onion peeled and diced
            
            
              1 frac12


              pounds ground beef like chuck or sirloin
            
            
              3


              cloves garlic peeled and minced
            
            
              2


              tablespoons ancho chile powder
            
            
